<m0>Citizens should stop<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 3.23 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>abusing parking spots<ql>
<m4>   LINE 2 IS 1.88 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>for the handicapped<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 3 IS 3.75 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.358 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
